The '''Corporate Alliance Directorate''', also referred to as the '''Alliance Exec board''', was the executive board of the [[Corporate Alliance/Legends|Corporate Alliance]]. [[Magistrate/Legends|Magistrate]] [[Passel Argente/Legends|Passel Argente]] led both the Alliance Directorate and the Corporate Alliance itself.

==History==
During the Clone Wars, [[Acquisitions Specialist]] [[Oro Dassyne/Legends|Oro Dassyne]] was promoted to the rank of [[General/Legends|general]] by Argente to serve in the armed forces of the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]].

